{"tid":647803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【深圳六成工業產品產量倒退】 【全靠華為、中興產品拉動工業生產】","createTime":"2018-04-30T06:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T02:55:02.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"df6fab3e7541cfccd45b9e8466a57c525bf3967e","tid":647803,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"早在2016年，深圳市政府就將華為與中興列為對深圳經濟貢獻最大的企業，單是華為的生產總值，就佔深圳總體GDP一成，這仍未計算依附著這兩公司生存的中、小型企業。<br />\n<br />\n2017年深圳市23種主要產品產量，有三分之二都處於大幅萎縮狀態，剩下仍保持增長的產品中，有7成半產值都是手機、集成電路、電子元件。這些都是華為和中興的主要產品，那如果華為和中興生產線出了問題，深圳的工業生產就幾乎出現全面倒退。<br />\n<br />\n2017年深圳GDP增長8.8%， 總產值首次超越香港。<br />\n<br />\n#華為中興是深圳經濟支柱<br />\n#深圳經濟<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1392745740991643/permalink/2024242237841987/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1392745740991643%2Fpermalink%2F2024242237841987%2F&d=c0IW%2Fu7PGTltYwpW2bMHqjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=36ba1647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1392745740991643/permalink/2024242237841987/</a>"},{"pid":"4ec9af33696f377d5f21782be51fdaf49ce5d256","tid":647803,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103cc22948e6dfe1b377ca16385cd00aa7ef69a4","tid":647803,"uid":2644,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"如果 FBI 隊冧 華為的話...<br />\n<br />\n分分鐘可以 Make 東莞 Great Again! <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.dailywire.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_full/public/uploads/2018/01/gettyimages-837567644.jpg?itok=TRua3Ydc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailywire.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Farticle_full%2Fpublic%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fgettyimages-837567644.jpg%3Fitok%3DTRua3Ydc&h=45f3d81d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"106db83476750c3aad4767a665f362997b29e85b","tid":647803,"uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬放生支那人，俾佢搵左咁多年污糟錢，等佢咁大枝野以為自己好醒，所謂自主研發都係偷呃拐騙，還記得華為賣廣告用單反影相出黎呃人話係電話影，做乜都要呃呃騙騙，所以非常支持侵總統叫佢自己交代賣左咩野俾禁售國，等佢又講大話就過癮喇，講真話又死講大話又死。<br />\n呢啲就叫多行不義必自斃，支那世界唔會有呢句野既。"},{"pid":"f0eed6ce0449045061ad4f1ec7726f181a19bacf","tid":647803,"uid":143621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9de9e1903b723d150e3da8805cd4d8c39f67976","tid":647803,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d787b7159238287233f045b56dead00373ac6f9","tid":647803,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4581cafbf10e1c706d457c9f1fc18f3ca5605b","tid":647803,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"Trump: ban 華為 is next for SURE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdd0e7676dbe653b500fa11017c6b6d813c22de","tid":647803,"uid":157138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"成日打晒飛機咁 原本個根本係咁脆弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7ebe5cf23b88fc17a042ba866fd5448fdeb709","tid":647803,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfdd0e7676dbe653b500fa11017c6b6d813c22de","tid":647803,"uid":157138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"成日打晒飛機咁 原本個根本係咁脆弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g